    "body": "I believe this is expected behavior, as formatter line lengths are usually not a hard requirement and can sometimes be exceed by 1 (or maybe even 2?) characters. It sounds like there are two feature requests here:\r\n\r\n1. Allow line_length to be a hard requirement\r\n2. Do not reformat \"properly\" formatted items (i.e. leave the second example alone, not sure of the best phrasing here)\r\n\r\nIf that's correct, let's close this and can you open separate feature requests for each?",
